CGI/Session/SQLite version 1.00
===============================

$Id: README,v 1.1 2004/10/15 15:29:29 bmoyles Exp $

CGI::Session::SQLite is a driver for CGI::Session allowing the use of a 
SQLite database on the back-end.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

CGI::Session
DBI
DBD::SQLite

